    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="tel:+40722744377" class="btn-primary cta">📞 Sună acum: 0722 744 377</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/40722744377?text=Salut%21%20Vreau%20o%20ofert%C4%83%20pentru%20animatori%20petrecere%20copii.%20Data%3A%20____%20Loca%C8%9Bie%3A%20____%20V%C3%A2rst%C4%83%3A%20____%20Nr.%20copii%3A%20____" class="btn-wa cta">💬 Scrie pe WhatsApp</a>
